<div class="aspects-editor-body">

  <p class="aspects-editor-hint">
    Enter one item per line. Use <code># Heading</code> for headings and <code>## Sub-heading</code> for sub-headings. All other lines are aspects.
  </p>

  <pre class="aspects-editor-example"><span class="aspects-editor-example-label">Example:</span>
# Scene Aspects
On Fire!
Slippery Floor

## Character Aspects — Alice
Reluctant Hero
Sharp Tongue</pre>

  <textarea
    name="aspectsText"
    class="aspects-editor-textarea"
    placeholder="# Scene Aspects&#10;On Fire!&#10;Slippery Floor"
    spellcheck="false"
  >{{aspectsText}}</textarea>

  <div class="aspects-editor-footer">
    <button type="button" data-action="saveAspects" class="aspects-btn aspects-btn--primary">
      <i class="fas fa-save"></i> Save Aspects
    </button>
  </div>

</div>
